                    "value": 2
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>Biran targets a creature with a specially crafted cocktail of chemicals to inhibit their performance. Biran makes a ranged injection rifle Strike; on a hit, the target takes damage as normal and must attempt a @Check[fortitude|dc:24] save.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature is @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Sickened]{Sickened 1}.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature is @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Slowed]{Slowed 1} for 1 round.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature is @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Sickened]{Sickened 2} and @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Slowed]{Slowed 2} for 1 round.</p>"
